Steps to run application
========================

1) Clone this repo
2) cd SamplePortal
3) Run 'npm install'
4) Edit .env file and set appropriate values for your MongoDB installation
   Defaults to localhost:27017/yelp
5) Run 'npm start'
6) Point your browser to http://localhost:3000

Available routes

/api/v1/business 
	GET A list of 20 random businesses sorted by name
/api/v1/business/:business_id 
	GET Details for a given business_id along with its associated reviews
/api/v1/facets
	GET Facet output by categories, stars, and price range
/api/v1/graph/:userId
	GET social graph output for given userId
